<Layout title='Plastering & Painting in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock Plastering & Painting Services' description='Plastering and painting contractors serving Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes. City & Guilds certified. No subcontractors.' activePage='home'>
