          <div style="padding-left:20px;border-left:3px solid #0C7BA8;">
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;">02</p>
