            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Every person on the team holds City &amp; Guilds certification. Victorian terrace plaster, new-build skims, high-end Venetian finishing — they've done it all.</p>
