            <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">It's us on your property. No one else.</h3>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We don't subcontract. The same team that quotes your job starts it and finishes it. What you're told on day one is what you get on day last.</p>
